I always find so much hope and inspiration in an amazing sunset.
This is the way I feel about the New Year. All is possible. Find your strength within, love yourself so that you can better love others.
Everyday look ahead and not behind.

The family dinner grace we have always said goes like this:

Father make us thankful for what we have 
And not self satisfied.
Let us give more that we get.
Let us love more than we hate.
Let us think of living more than having lived.

Happy New Year!

#happynewyear #happynewyear2023 #lovemorethanever #live #liveauthentic

We added our kitchen onto our 1850’s stone farmhouse 19 years ago. My goal was to make the addition timeless, whereby someone walking through the house would not realize that they had left the old part and entered the new. I also wanted it to be a kitchen that would not just be following a trend that would become dated with in 7 years. I am proud to say that our kitchen is still relevant.
The island was custom made for us by @hoffmanandwoodward .
Our kitchen is not only still relevant, the @benjaminmoore Gloucester Sage paint on the cabinets that I chose way back then, was one of their color trends in 2022. 
I still love our kitchen, it is the space we live in the most.
Cooking around the island as we visit is what we love most!
#loveyourhabitat #kitchen #kitchendesign #benjaminmoore #timeless #timelessdesign #stonefarmhouse #oldhouses #starbrightfarm

On average, one spends 2,569 hours in their bed a year! You better LOVE your bedding!
I LOVE this @libeco_home duvet.  There is something about the feel and weight of the 100 %linen. A softness. The weave is stunning and I can wash in my machine.
Even Mark has repeatedly commented on how much he loves it!
It mixes well with the layers of pillows of different fabtics.
Pillow fabrics : @laurenliess , @heatherchadduck , 
This bed finds a good balance between feminine and masculine so we are both happy!
DM me if you are interested in this duvet cover.
Twin and queen readily available, king available for preorder and can ship June 1.
If you are not familiar with Libeco linens, head to their website and read about the process of linen. Fascinating.
#lovelinen #bedding #duvetcover #duvetcover #bedrooms #belgiumlinen

Now as an empty nester she started @rellebeebags . She designs these amazing bags ( pictured here is the “Sling” ) and then they are all made rt here in Baltimore and some in Pa. They are functional and fashionable. Totally cool gal making cool stuff!
We carry them in our @starbrightfarm Barn Market. #rellebeebags #handmade #smallbatch #unique #oneofakind #soulsister #friends

Did a little porch makeover this summer. Nothing major but I love the results.
Biggest thing was to get a REAL light with fans! Game changer having lights that work and fans for the breeze @rejuvenation ( the old wires were up in the ceiling in no electrical box 😳🤔 and we wondered why they shorted out!! Lucky we didn’t have a fire! )
Next I decided that (after 29 years) I was sick of the shabby chic look of the rusting white wrought iron furniture so a little wire brushing and 8 cans of @rustoleum they are now black!
I had new cushions made but went with a similar look of the charcoal grey stripe @sunbrella 
I saved a couple of the old cushions for the dogs to lie on! ( seen under the sofa)
I also purchased 2 lightweight simple black outdoor wicker chairs so that we could bring them over to the conversation area when we have guests.
Loving the way the grey plant stand looks with my topiaries.
@atlockfarm brings them for me to sell in our @starbrightfarm  Barn Market, but I always grab a few for myself 😍
After about 3 years of neglecting my porch, I love it again!!
#optoutside #porch #porchdecor #remodel #makeover #paintedfurniture #frontporch #porchlife #countryliving #outsideliving #ceilingfan
